{
  "texts": [
    "Beyond general satisfaction, sentiment analysis can explore patient experiences with specific treatments.",
    "By analyzing discussions about pharmaceuticals, vaccines, or therapies, researchers assess real-world patient perceptions of effectiveness, side effects, and value (10, 29).",
    "Such analysis of online drug reviews may help identify unreported adverse drug reactions contributing to pharmacovigilance (29).",
    "LLMs are also being explored to analyze patient feedback.",
    "For instance, ChatGPT has been used for aspect-based sentiment analysis of patient reviews to assess dissatisfaction with different aspects of care, like physician skills or infrastructure (40)."
  ]
}